This paper deals with neural network pruning and adaptation techniques for improving the generalization capacity of a model. The task of automatic speech recognition is used as an example to demonstrate the effectiveness of the proposed approach. Therefore, the most likely sub-category is cs.CL (Computation and Language), followed by cs.LG (Machine Learning), cs.CV (Computer Vision and Pattern Recognition), cs.SD (Sound), and cs.AI (Artificial Intelligence).
